videos.headline: Georgia Tech strikes first with fumble recovery TD
videos.description: N'Kosi Perry is sacked in the end zone and fumbles the ball, and Ja'Quon Griffin recovers it for the Yellow Jackets touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Georgia Tech strikes first with fumble recovery TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Miami scores on QB sneak
videos.description: N'Kosi Perry runs one yard into the end zone to tie the game at 7-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Miami scores on QB sneak) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Osborn stretches into end zone for Miami TD
videos.description: N'Kosi Perry finds K.J. Osborn, who reaches into the end zone for a 13-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Osborn stretches into end zone for Miami TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Georgia Tech scores on fake punt
videos.description: Georgia Tech punter Pressley Harvin III fakes a punt and goes deep to Nathan Cottrell, who scores a 41-yard touchdown for Georgia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Harvin connects with Cottrell for 41-yard TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Harris breaks through for 19-yard touchdown
videos.description: N'Kosi Perry finds Cam'Ron Harris, who weaves through defenders for a 19-yard Miami touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Harris breaks through for 19-yard touchdown) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Graham connects with Brown for 35-yard TD
videos.description: James Graham makes a long throw in traffic and Ahmarean Brown catches it in the end zone for a Georgia Tech touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Graham connects with Brown for 35-yard TD) 2019/10/19
